<br>
At that point several &quot;friends&quot; of ours that couldn't or wouldn't get into most of guilds on server were also &quot;hanging&quot; with us and getting some loots/spells from us in process. Namely Despondency and Vaamp. Those (Desp. and Vaamp) got in close with Erdrick. Despondency then said he would like to trade his bard for a wizard, they exchanged pwords and Despondency then changed pw on both accounts. Since that person bought Erdrick to begin with, he could not recover pw. and left RZ as far as I am concerned.<br>
<br>
Later on, Erdrick was used to pvp MiM to some extent (not much and he never had DoZ tag because me and esp. Gloryia strongly disapproved of the way acct. was aquired) and then was guilded in Eximos and access was supposedly given to Gbak.<br>
<br>
Gbak then ninjalooted Tunare on Erdrick and deguilded from Eximos? I do have screenshot of Erdrick telling me its Gbak, but he claimed the warrior was banned. So honestly I think wiz. is still controlled by either Despondency or Vaamp to stir shit against us.<br>
<br>
The whole thing is one big mess. The problem with unkosing acct. is the fact that it changed so many hands in such questionable ways that there's no way to know who did what on that character.<br>
<br>
So, whos driving erdrick now and how did you aquire acct. kind sir?<br>
<br>
